OL,3,CLucy Letby inquiry will not be live-
OL,4,Cstreamed to public
OL,6,FAn inquiry into the crimes of serial
OL,7,Fkiller nurse Lucy Letby will not be
OL,8,Flivestreamed to the public, it has
OL,9,Fbeen ruled.
OL,11,FThe inquiry, which will examine how
OL,12,Fthe nurse was able to murder babies on
OL,13,Fthe Countess of Chester Hospital's
OL,14,Fneonatal unit in 2015 and 2016, is set
OL,15,Fto begin at Liverpool Town Hall on
OL,16,FSeptember 10.
