OL,3,CLucy Letby inquiry will not be live-
OL,4,Cstreamed to public
OL,6,FLetby, of Hereford, was sentenced to
OL,7,F14 whole life orders after she was
OL,8,Fconvicted of murdering seven babies
OL,9,Fand attempting to murder six others,
OL,10,Fwith two attempts on one of her
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,FLawyers for the families had argued
OL,14,Fthat the inquiry should be
OL,15,Flivestreamed to the public to prevent
OL,16,Fthe spread of "grossly offensive"
OL,17,Fconspiracy theories.
