OL,3,CLucy Letby inquiry will not be live-
OL,4,Cstreamed to public
OL,6,FIn a ruling published on Wednesday,
OL,7,Fchairwoman of the inquiry Lady Justice
OL,8,FThirlwall said the proceedings would
OL,9,Fnot be broadcast live because of the
OL,10,Frisk of breaching court orders which
OL,11,Fprevent the identification of a number
OL,12,Fof people involved, including all of
OL,13,Fthe babies.
OL,15,FShe said: "I do not accept that this
OL,16,Fis a risk the inquiry should take. Not
OL,17,Fonly is there a significant risk to
OL,18,Fthe inquiry itself, I take account of
OL,19,Fthe human cost of a breach.
