OL,6,F"For a parent, who has already
OL,7,Fsuffered so much, to be identified
OL,8,Fonline is unthinkable."
OL,10,FThe hearings will be held in public
OL,11,Fand those involved in the inquiry,
OL,12,Fincluding the families and media, will
OL,13,Fbe able to apply to watch remotely
OL,14,Fover live links.
