OL,6,FIn her ruling, Lady Justice Thirlwall
OL,7,Frejected the submissions from lawyers
OL,8,Frepresenting the families, made at a
OL,9,Fpreliminary hearing earlier this
OL,10,Fmonth, that a publicly available live
OL,11,Fbroadcast would "reduce or dispel
OL,12,Ftoxic and offensive conspiracy
OL,13,Ftheories".
OL,15,FShe said: "Searching for truth is not
OL,16,Fa characteristic of conspiracy
OL,17,Ftheorists. Like those who promulgate
OL,18,Ffake news, they search for information
OL,19,Fwhich supports their world view.
