OL,6,F"When they find none, they manufacture
OL,7,Fit, often using and distorting video
OL,8,Ffootage to be found on the internet."
OL,10,FShe said it was "unsurprising" that
OL,11,Fstaff at the hospital were anxious and
OL,12,Fconcerned about giving evidence to the
OL,13,Finquiry.
