OL,6,FShe added: "I make it plain that,
OL,7,Fnotwithstanding their nerves, I expect
OL,8,Fall witnesses, doctors and nurses
OL,9,Fincluded, to tell the truth, to make
OL,10,Fevery effort to assist the inquiry
OL,11,Fwhen giving evidence and to reflect
OL,12,Fthoughtfully on what happened. Candour
OL,13,Fand frankness should be a given."
